Title: Fix broken link in README file

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Go to the project's README file on GitHub.
2. Click on the link to the documentation.
3. The page displays a 404 error message.
Expected Result: The link should lead to the correct documentation page without any errors.
Actual Result: The link is broken and leads to an error page.
